  "title": "Refuse Truck Driver",
  "description": "<p>🚛 Join Our Team as a Waste Collection Driver (Class 4)! 🚛 Be part of a team that keeps the city clean and green – with great benefits and a positive work culture!</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Collect and transport general waste and recyclables safely and efficiently to disposal and recycling facilities while maintaining vehicle condition and contributing to a positive team environment.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Collect general waste and recyclables accurately from various customer locations to ensure timely service</li><li>Transport waste safely from the warehouse to designated disposal and recycling facilities following all safety protocols</li><li>Maintain the cleanliness, condition, and safety of your vehicle daily to support operational reliability</li><li>Collaborate with team members to meet collection schedules and uphold service quality standards</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Hold a valid Class 4 driving license to operate waste collection vehicles safely</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Apply hooklift operation skills to load and unload waste containers efficiently (training provided if no prior experience)</li><li>Demonstrate friendly, responsible, and motivated teamwork to foster a positive and productive work environment</li></ul>",
